Special Notice for Educational Use:

This software is specifically designed for educational institutions in Zambia 
and other developing countries. While the MIT license allows commercial use, 
we encourage:

1. Free use for public schools and educational institutions
2. Contribution back to the community through improvements and feedback
3. Respect for the cultural and linguistic adaptations made for Zambian schools
4. Consideration of the rural and resource-constrained context this was built for

For commercial implementations, please consider supporting rural education 
initiatives in Zambia or contributing to the ongoing development of this platform.

Contact: bernardzulu23@github.com
